dogecoin.text:
7/ The World's most valuable Joke -
The current market cap of the Dogecoin is $80 Billion. And, it's worth more than these corporate giants -
•Ford 🚘
•Twitter 🐦
•Airbus ✈️
The Doge is bigger than Oil giants, car makers, software companies, aerospace companies.

5/ The Doge to the Moon - 🌛
From using a mock Vogue cover, dubbed "Dogue" to calling himself "Dogefather", the billionaire Tesla and SpaceX CEO (Elon Musk) has spent years talking up the token. On Feb 4, Dogecoin surged more than 50% after Musk tweeted his suppot for it.

4/ The Doge Appreciation -
Today, Dogecoin is used as a tipping system on Reddit and Twitter to reward quality content, comments, for performing good deeds.

3/ The Rise - 🔼
Soon Redditors were using their collective power for fundraising, successfully raising enough of the cryptocurrency for publicity stunts like sponsoring a Nascar driver etc. which reportedly led to rise in Dogecoin's market cap to over $90 million within a year.

1/ Who let the Doge out? 🪙
In 2013, Dogecoin was started as a joke between IBM software engineer Billy Markus and Adobe software engineer Jackson Palmer.
#DogecoinRise #dogecoin #memecoin

How Dogecoin went from a Meme to the fourth largest cryptocurrency ?
